&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You’ll Never Want to Leave&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot; data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Respect People. Produce Results.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;For more than 35 years, we’ve built a reputation for both the work we do and how we do it.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Respect shows up in how we work together and with our clients. It means trusting people to do their jobs, giving them the space to do it well, and holding each other to a high standard. Because when people are respected, they do better work, work that grows businesses, shapes culture, and builds relationships that last. And just as important, they have the support to build a career and a life worth investing in.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Helping Achieve &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RPA is seeking an Analyst to join the Analytics and Insights team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;re not an Analyst...you&#39;re an amazing storyteller. OK, you&#39;re an Analyst. But you can tell extraordinary stories with data, and that is what we are looking for. If you enjoy numbers and are a critical thinker that can multi-task, work in team settings, produce high quality work with minimal supervision, then you may have just found your dream job.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Working On&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key player for the Honda/Acura research and analytics practice overseeing campaign measurement plans, goal setting, and insights across all media channels (online and offline)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborating with internal teams at RPA and Honda/Acura clients to analyze data from multiple sources in order to tell the most effective story (programmatic, social media, etc.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Building and presenting client and executive facing visuals, tying results back to business and marketing objectives&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You’ll Excel In Your Role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1-2 years analytics experience with a focus on advertising &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency using Microsoft Excel for analysis, charting, and automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience visualizing client deliverables data within PowerPoint or Tableau&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with unrefined data using a variety of analytical and statistical toolsets (e.g., Excel, SQL, or other BI Tools)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Self-starter who is resourceful, collaborative, and able to run with something given minimal direction&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Must be comfortable working in a fast-paced environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clear and straightforward written and verbal communicator with a genuine zest for numbers/analytics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong organization, project management, and time management skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong client management skills, ability to prioritize requests alongside regular deliverables&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eager to learn new skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4256&quot; data-end=&quot;4320&quot;&gt;We are unable to offer employment visa assistance for this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4322&quot; data-end=&quot;4429&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;4322&quot; data-end=&quot;4427&quot;&gt;The annual salary for this position is $71,000

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;General Creative Submission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Los Angeles (Hybrid) | Open to Exceptional Talent Everywhere&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department:&lt;/strong&gt; Creative&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Don’t See the Right Role? Show Us Your Work Anyway.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At RPA, we’re always looking for curious thinkers, fearless makers, and people who believe creativity can move business — and culture — forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you don’t see an open role that fits your background but believe your work belongs here, we’d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This posting is for designers, writers, art directors, ACDs, CDs, content creators, social strategists, editors, motion designers, and creative hybrids of all kinds who want to be considered for future opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re interested in creatives who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Think strategically and execute beautifully&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring original ideas, not just polished decks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Know how to collaborate across disciplines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Care about craft as much as concept&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand brands — and how to push them forward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are comfortable working across platforms (social, digital, film, experiential, integrated campaigns)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether your background is traditional, digital-first, social-native, culturally driven, or something we haven’t seen yet — we want to see what you make.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What to Send&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portfolio link (required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resume or LinkedIn profile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A brief note about what kind of work excites you and what role you’re hoping to grow into&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If your work aligns with an upcoming need, our Talent team will reach out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why RPA?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re an independent agency built on the belief that people come first — and the best ideas come from empowered teams. We partner with ambitious brands and create work that drives results and earns attention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re committed to building a team with diverse backgrounds, perspectives, and experiences. The more voices at the table, the better the work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Even if the timing isn’t right today, we’re always building relationships for tomorrow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let’s make something great.&lt;/p&gt;

