&lt;p&gt;Every day, you’ll be teaming up with a diverse, enthusiastic, multi-disciplinary team of professionals with a smart sense of humor and a strong desire to grow and develop.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Local Media Buyer, Dallas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RPA is seeking a detail-oriented and proactive Local Media Negotiator to join our Dallas team to aid in planning, negotiating, and executing media campaigns across local markets. This role is responsible for managing buys across television, radio, streaming, and emerging platforms, ensuring campaigns deliver efficiently and perform against client goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position requires strong analytical skills, attention to detail, and the ability to manage multiple campaigns.&lt;/p&gt;
