&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute local media plans across TV, radio, streaming, and emerging platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide POVs and recommendations for packages, such as Sports, News and community event sponsorships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee budgets by market (DMA), channel, and daypart based on campaign objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate rates, placements, and added value with local vendors and station representatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Secure inventory and manage buys in competitive markets, including high-demand periods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain media schedules and ensure seamless execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor campaign delivery, pacing, and performance against KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track ratings, impressions, and cost metrics (CPP, CPM, etc.) to optimize campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze Nielsen data and market-level trends to inform decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify underperformance and proactively adjust buys mid-flight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage post logs, affidavits, and invoice reconciliation; secure makegoods and under delivery weight as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain strong vendor relationships while holding partners accountable to performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with strategy, account, finance and traffic teams for integrated campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate campaign updates, insights, and recommendations clearly to internal teams and clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
