&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Helping Achieve&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;RPA is seeking a Senior Digital Analyst to join our Analytics team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More than just working with data, this role is for someone who knows how to turn data into a story people actually understand and can act on. The ideal candidate brings analytical rigor, creative problem-solving, and practical business sense to the work, with experience across web and email analytics and confidence in both reporting and implementation. They also have a natural curiosity for how AI can improve the way we think, work, and uncover insights.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Working On&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver ongoing performance reports, translating data into insights and recommendations for business executives and digital stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct deep-dive analyses (e.g. A/B testing, audience segmentation, campaign performance, pre/post redesigns) to uncover trends and opportunities that drive optimization and growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor performance and data quality, proactively identifying and flagging any issues to the appropriate teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to measurement strategy across brands, including measurement planning, goal setting, testing strategies, and performance evaluation across web and email&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional partners to analyze channel performance, inform strategy, improve user experience, and optimize marketing and analytics initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support analytics implementation across websites and applications:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop tagging documentation aligned with business requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct UAT for analytics tags in staging and production environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, troubleshoot, and communicate tagging issues to relevant teams (e.g. account, media, tech, web dev, engineering, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expand analytics capabilities through forecasting, automation, and business intelligence solutions, including the development of internal and leadership dashboards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help shape an “AI-ready” analytics ecosystem by integrating AI into our data workflows, measurement, and governance practices
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft, test, and refine generative AI prompts to support accurate and thoughtful analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a shared library of prompts, use cases, and best practices to enable consistent, high-quality outputs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply a test-and-learn approach, iterating, evaluating, and validating outputs to ensure they are grounded in strong data and sound judgment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
